---
title: Shrimp Spaghetti & Zucchini in Marinara Sauce
description: When the craving strikes, nothing but a cozy bowl of pasta with homemade tomato sauce will do. You’ll simmer up succulent herbed shrimp in a pan of garlicky red sauce with sautéed zucchini, then toss in spaghetti and serve with a sprinkle of zippy scallion greens for an extra pop of color. Best of all, you’re ready to eat in less than half an hour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ba31af36661f46803905f4-0e7be029.jpeg
